def_cn: 与…一起存在；与…不可分离
def_en: If one thing goes with another thing, the two things officially belong together, so that if you get one, you also get the other.
If one thing goes with another thing, it is usually found or experienced together with the other thing.

def_cn: 与（异性）交往；和…谈恋爱（或保持性关系）
def_en: If someone is going with another person, they are having a sexual or romantic relationship with that person.
